{"tid":2450316,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鮭魚之亂｜名有「鮭魚」全枱免費！ 壽司郎優惠掀台人改名熱 全名36字破紀錄","createTime":"2021-03-17T09:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T12:34:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a11d388baad33198fa7236aedc796f16a5bcf486","tid":2450316,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"日本過江龍「壽司郎」在香港大排長龍，而在一岸之隔的台灣，壽司郎就推出速銷活動，只要姓名中有「鮭魚」（香港稱三文魚）同音同字的顧客，就能於17及18日到店享用「全桌免費」的優惠，引發不少當地網民質疑：「誰真的會叫鮭魚？」但令人意想不到的是，台北市至少有20名市民趕在16及17日改名叫「鮭魚」，而台中12區的戶政事務所也接獲多人查問改名手續，目前已有15人改名「鮭魚」，還有「鮭魚丼飯」、「鮭魚肚」、「潘同鮭魚盡」等名字，無奇不有。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210317/SPNWIHI2FVDFTCOY2DKYDUZCQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210317%2FSPNWIHI2FVDFTCOY2DKYDUZCQQ%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTzXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=773e348e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210317%2FSPNWIHI2FVDFTCOY2DKYDUZCQQ%2F&h=9ccf708f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210317/SPNWIHI2FVDFTCOY2DKYDUZCQQ/</a>"},{"pid":"ee572ea4cf010ad7e67cb2a3031310bdd9379389","tid":2450316,"uid":225549,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"日本人好尊重三文魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c933464e9b5a6f56f56f35d6cf10e4b1728433fa","tid":2450316,"uid":54437,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"睇嚟台灣政府做野幾有效率<br />\n咁快改完"},{"pid":"74fe63bed9c6e7ce0be332ac03c7c33e509899a4","tid":2450316,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:05:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://travel.ettoday.net/article/1940388.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ettoday.net%2Farticle%2F1940388.htm&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTzXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=f